channel.description: Your task is to build a website that shows astronauts fetched from an API. Get Started Take a look at the starter code for the following studio located here: javascript-projects/fetch/studio Requirements Add code that runs on the window load event. This is done because we canâ€™t interact with the HTML elements until the page has loaded. Make a GET request using fetch to the astronauts API <https://handlers.education.launchcode.org/static/astronauts.json>__
